Cliffjumper transformed. He had a mean look in his eyes. "Are you
Maximal?" He asked, as he trained his gun on Gimmler.

Headstrong and Firedrill lay on the ground motionless. They both began
to stir, Headstrong reaching for his sword, and Firedrill for him. "Give
it up *SNORT* Autobot. It's over" he yelled as they began to strugle
again.
